sdp/prd-cypherclaw-v2-2026-05-22.md:471:| CC-104 | Depends on CC-040 through CC-048 and CC-102. Render a 60-second reference sample with `CYPHERCLAW_V2_TUNING_MORPH=1` (5-limit JI for Listen, Slendro for Conversation, with a morph at the transition), upload as `cypherclaw/archive/checkpoints/feature-5-tuning-morph-{timestamp}/` with both flag-on and flag-off A/B excerpts, send a Telegram notification with the archive URL, and pause until APPROVE / REWORK / REJECT. | MUST | T1 | Task transitions to APPROVED only after explicit operator verdict; both A/B excerpts are retrievable from the archive feed; tuning shift is audible. |
